data.value:
Andrej Tetkic is a skilled Blender artist and developer known for creating various add-ons that enhance the functionality and user experience of Blender. He specializes in developing tools that streamline workflows, such as the "Drag and Drop Import" add-on, which simplifies the process of importing files into Blender by allowing users to drag and drop files directly into the 3D viewport. Tetkic's contributions are widely appreciated in the Blender community for improving efficiency and ease of use
